Class ExportReportFeatures<T extends InputFromManager,S,U>

  • Object
    • AnchorBean<Task<T,S>>
      • Task<T,S>
        • ExportReportFeatures<T,S,U>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - input-object type
    S - shared-state type
    U - feature-type
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    ExportReportFeaturesFromManifest, ExportReportFeaturesFromMulti

    public abstract class ExportReportFeatures<T extends InputFromManager,S,U>
extends Task<T,S>
    A base class for tasks that calculate and export ReportFeatures.

    The following outputs are produced:

    Output NameDefault?Description
    featureReportyesA CSV file with the report-features as columns (and an ID column), one for each input.
